---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const updated = 'June 2026';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Whisp"
  description="Whisp privacy policy. We take your data and your inner life seriously."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container legal-body">
    <div class="legal-content">

      <p class="lead">Your inner life is private. We treat it that way.</p>

      <h2>1. What we collect</h2>
      <p>When you use Whisp, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account information:</strong> email address and display name when you create an account.</li>
        <li><strong>Journal content:</strong> sign logs, dreams, symbols, notes, and entries you create in the app. This data is stored in your private account and is not shared with other users.</li>
        <li><strong>Beliefs and preferences:</strong> the cosmological frameworks you select (astrology, numerology, etc.) to personalize AI responses.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> basic analytics like app opens and feature usage, collected in aggregate, not linked to your journal content.</li>
        <li><strong>Device information:</strong> device type, OS version, and app version for debugging and support.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How we use your data</h2>
      <p>We use your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide and improve the Whisp service</li>
        <li>Generate personalized AI reflections and pattern insights</li>
        <li>Send transactional emails (account confirmations, subscription receipts)</li>
        <li>Respond to support requests</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>We do not sell your data.</strong> We do not share your journal content with third parties for advertising or marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>3. AI and third-party services</h2>
      <p>
        Whisp uses Claude (Anthropic) to generate personalized reflections. When you request an AI insight,
        relevant portions of your journal data are sent to Anthropic's API to generate a response.
        Anthropic's use of this data is governed by their <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-link">privacy policy</a>.
        We use API access, which means your data is not used to train Anthropic's models.
      </p>
      <p>We also use:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Firebase (Google):</strong> for authentication, database, and storage.</li>
        <li><strong>PostHog:</strong> for first-party usage analytics (app opens, feature usage). PostHog collects anonymized event data and does not have access to your journal content. We do not use advertising identifiers.</li>
        <li><strong>Adapty:</strong> for subscription management.</li>
        <li><strong>Stripe:</strong> for payment processing. We do not store payment card details.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        Your journal data is retained as long as your account is active. You may delete your account
        and all associated data at any time from the app settings. Deletion is permanent and irreversible.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Security</h2>
      <p>
        All data is encrypted in transit and at rest. We use Firebase's security infrastructure and
        follow industry best practices. No system is perfectly secure; we will notify you promptly
        in the event of any breach affecting your data.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Export your journal data</li>
        <li>Delete your account and all data</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate account information</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@eyeswidewellness.com" class="inline-link">hello@eyeswidewellness.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>7. Children</h2>
      <p>Whisp is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy periodically. Material changes will be communicated via email or in-app notification. Continued use of Whisp after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Reach us at:
        <a href="mailto:hello@eyeswidewellness.com" class="inline-link">hello@eyeswidewellness.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 160px 0 64px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--navy-border);
  }
  .page-hero .section-label { display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .page-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(200,196,184,0.35);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .legal-body { padding: 64px 0 120px; }
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .legal-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .legal-content p, .legal-content li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
  .legal-content ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .legal-content strong { color: var(--cream); font-weight: 500; }
  .inline-link {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
  }
  .inline-link:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
</style>
